    Most of Mexico will no longer observe DST
    
    Also, Chihuahua moves to year-round -06.
    * NEWS: Mention this.
    * northamerica (Mexico): No DST after 2022.
    (America/Ojinaga, America/Chihuahua): Switch from -07 to -06
    on 2022-10-30 02:00.

